    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick)<strong> </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Squeeze your <strong>sausage</strong> <strong>meat </strong>from the skins into the pan (clean hands is the best way!) and discard the skins</p><p>Break the <strong>sausage</strong> <strong>meat</strong> up into bite-sized pieces with a wooden spoon, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> and cook for 5-7 min or until the sausage meat has browned and the onion has softened</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1688738566494-x200.jpg",
