            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>green chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a small bowl with <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>herby chilli dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1688738569740-x200.jpg",
