    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sausage meat has browned, add the <strong>diced pepper </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook for a further 2-3 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>drained potatoes </strong>and cook, stirring occasionally, for 5-6 min or until golden and the sausage meat has cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
